title: VIDEO: Sen. Ron Johnson talks issues with Columbus High School students

maintext: Sen. Ron Johnson (R-Wisconsin) visited Columbus High School students Friday at the school library. Johnson discussed a variety of topics and fielded questions from the students for more than an hour.
